<p>This study expands its analysis to include a sample of 90 more recent deals (closed in 2021) managed by 46 managers, using the Morningstar European Euro Denominated Loan Index as the benchmark loan index.</p>
<p>The table in this article illustrates the relative standing of each EU CLO manager based on their latest average total alpha metrics. A score of 98%, for instance, indicates that the manager’s total return alpha is at the 98th percentile, meaning their total return alpha metric is greater than or equal to 98% of their peers.</p>
